data.description: One of the most spectacular and private properties anywhere in the Pacific Northwest! .6 acres including an extra lot for privacy or investment plus backing onto acreage. The owners have painstakingly and lovingly created the ultimate private park with thousands of plantings, a large pond with triple waterfall, private paths winding through the gardens & tall evergreens to secret & enchanting sitting areas. The spectacular & large deck area is spilt into 2 areas & has large covered areas for lounging, entertaining, or bird watching. The home boasts vaulted ceilings, skylights, expansive windows overlooking the gardens, 3 bedrooms plus office and wonderful architectural features. This property is simply irreplaceable & will not disappoint!!
